# Pretty URLs (/privacy, /terms, /support → /privacy.html, /terms.html, /support.html)
# are handled automatically by Workers Static Assets html_handling=auto-trailing-slash.
# No rule needed here; adding one creates a redirect loop with the built-in canonicalisation.

# Legacy markdown links (App Store Connect / GitHub README) → new clean URLs.
/PRIVACY.md     /privacy        301
/TERMS.md       /terms          301
/SUPPORT.md     /support        301
/PRIVACY_EN.md  /privacy?lang=en  301
/TERMS_EN.md    /terms?lang=en    301
/SUPPORT_EN.md  /support?lang=en  301

# www → apex is handled by a Cloudflare Bulk Redirect / Page Rule
# on the zone (absolute URLs are disallowed inside _redirects).
